_source.title: System_Swaping
_source.visState: {"title":"System_Swaping","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(index=sar*, metric=avg:pswpin/s).if(eq, 0, null, .es(metric=avg:pswpin/s)).bars(width=40).label(\"Swap In\").color(\"#FF0000\"),\n.es(index=sar*, metric=avg:pswpout/s).if(eq, 0, null, .es(metric=avg:pswpout/s)).bars(width=40).label(\"Swap Out\").color(\"#AA0000\").title('Memory paging activity')","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}

_source.title: System_CPU
_source.visState:
{"title":"System_CPU","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: CPU AND component: all', metric=avg:%user).bars(width=40).label("%User").color("#00FF00"),
.es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: CPU AND component: all', metric=avg:%system).bars(width=40).label("%System").color("#0000FF"),
.es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: CPU AND component: all', metric=avg:%iowait).bars(width=40).label("%IOWait").color("#FF0000")
.title("CPU over time")","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}

_source.title: System_Disk_IO
_source.visState: {"title":"System_Disk_IO","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: system', metric=avg:rtps).if(eq, 0, null, .es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: system', metric=avg:rtps).fit(average)).label('Reads/s'),\n.es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: system', metric=avg:wtps).if(eq, 0, null, .es(index=sar*, q='hostname: * AND metric_name: system', metric=avg:wtps).fit(average)).label('Writes/s').title(\"Disk I/O\")","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}

_source.title: System_Disk_IO_Top5
_source.visState: {"title":"System_Disk_IO_Top5","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(index=sar*,  q='hostname: * AND metric_name: DEV', metric=avg:tps, split=component.keyword:5).bars(width=40).label(\"dev [$1]\", \"^.* > component.keyword:(\\S+) > .*\").title('Top 5 Disks')","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}

_source.title: System_Net
_source.visState: {"title":"System_Net","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(index=sar*,  metric=avg:rxbyt/s).if(eq, 0, null, .es( metric=avg:rxbyt/s).fit(average)).label('readKBs/s') , .es(index=sar*,  metric=avg:txbyt/s).if(eq, 0, null, .es( metric=avg:txbyt/s).fit(average)).label('writeKB/s').title('Network activity over time')","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}
